data.description: Move-In-Ready, Spacious home on an oversized lot! open living room & dining room, along with all 5 bedrooms. counter space, new kitchen with granite counter top. 2.1/2 car ATTACHED garage for the cold winters, getting the groceries to the kitchen, or even converting to future living space, This split-level home in Hazel Crest is situated on a quiet well-kept block close to schools, transportation, and parks. Enjoy the awesome back yard that the huge corner lot allows. Inside, enjoy the spacious living room with oversized windows, a dining room with sliding glass doors that lead out to a patio, All bedrooms are generously proportioned.  Great home with plenty of room to grow into and make your own.
